                        <summary>
                            
                            <p>On the west base of the <hi rend="italic">gōpura</hi> of the first <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> of Chandramaulīśvara temple.</p>						
                            
                            <p>Śōbhakṛit.</p>						
                            
                            <p>This inscription engraved in late characters records the fixation of the levy on looms at 1/4 <hi rend="italic">paṇam</hi> per loom and the resettlement of the weaver community after there had been a quarrel between the various communities, by Nāga Raḍḍiyār and Liṅgā Raḍḍiyār of Śri Naraśā-Paṇḍitar-nāḍu.</p>						
                            
                        </summary>
                    </msContents>
